hmm how do i use agent mode in my crafting env? :sweat_smile:

i tested that my fixes work for creating multiple classes at once using prebuilt classes

but whenever i try to use `POST /autogenerate-schema`, i get this error
```Missing key inputs argument! To use the Google AI API, provide (`api_key`) arguments. To use the Google Cloud API, provide (`vertexai`, `project` & `location`) arguments.\n\n METADATA:\n\n\n{}```
ooh yup, u need to add GEMINI_API_KEY in your env overrides file and the acc key is in 1pass

thanks @ayesha.ali!

i tested autogenerating schema with split classification on my branch, and there's only 1 `POST /schema` call! :tada:
